Everything in here is a Tcl module.  Add this directory to your ::tcl::tm::path and enjoy.


fun-0.tm        -- lots of useful routines for functional style and brevity in Tcl
    notable: many things.  Read it over a cup of tea.

extend-0.tm     -- many extensions (extra subcommands) for Tcl builtins.  Some essential, some questionable.

chans-0.tm      -- a small collection of handy refchan/transchans
    notable:  [chan push stdout [list teecmd {.textwidget insert end}]]

debug-0.tm      -- a debugging library
    notable:  debug log {substmessage};  debug assert {expr} {substmessage}

tests-0.tm      -- self-contained tests within packages

options-0.tm    -- [options] and [arguments] for procs
    this is somewhat popular

tip288-0.tm     -- an extension on the above providing prefix/infix optional arguments

pkg-0.tm        -- simple packages

tsv-0.1.tm      -- more flexible replacement for tcllib's csv

oometa-1.tm     -- TclOO extension done right!  (a literate program)
    please steal and use this.  It needs examples.

totp-0.tm       -- simple totp/hotp implementation

tdbcplus-0.1.tm -- monkey patches for TDBC.  Illustrates [mixin] well.

sql-0.tm        -- helpers for safely composing SQL queries

snidgets/       -- various (mega-)widgets using the wonderful snit
